an></x-group> of the <x-word word="vine"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #FF0000;">vine</span></x-word> among the trees of the forest as fuel for the fire, so will I treat the people living in <x-word word="jerusalem"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #FF0000;">Jerusalem</span></x-word>.<br>所以主耶和华如此说：众树以内的葡萄树，我怎样使它在火中当柴，也必照样待耶路撒冷的居民。<br><br><br>结15:7 <br>I will set my face against them. Although they have come out of the fire, the fire will yet consume them. And when I set my face against them, you will know that I am the LORD.<br>我必向他们变脸，他们虽从火中出来，火却要烧灭他们。我向他们变脸的时候，你们就知道我是耶和华。<br><br><br>结15:8 <br>I will make the land <x-word word="desolate"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #FF0000;">desolate</span></x-word> because they have been <x-word word="unfaithful"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #800000;">unfaithful</span></x-word>, declares the <x-word word="sovereign"><span style="border-bottom:1px solid #FF0000;">Sovereign</span></x-word> LORD."<br>我必使地土荒凉，因为他们行事干犯我。这是主耶和华说的。”</p>

